import React from 'react';
import { Container, Form, FloatingLabel, Button} from 'react-bootstrap';

export default function GoodsForm(){
    return(
        <Container>
            <Form>
                <FloatingLabel
                    controlId="floatingInput"
                    label="Enter product name"
                    className="mb-3"
                >
                    <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter product name" />
                </FloatingLabel>
                <FloatingLabel controlId="floatingQuantity" label="Enter the quantity of goods">
                    <Form.Control type="number" placeholder="Enter the quantity of goods" />
                </FloatingLabel>
                <Button></Button>
            </Form>
        </Container>
    )
}
